  "detailed_description": "<strong>Keali includes</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Six to Ten hours of content.<br></li><li> Extra challenges in the form of Mural Fragments that unlock secrets of the past.<br></li><li> Leaderboards to race friends and strangers.<br></li><li> A complex and engaging movement system with a high skill ceiling for you to explore and master.<br></li><li> Unique levels that explore custom platforms, threats, and puzzles.<br></li><li> Levels have multiple solutions, some easier than others.<br></li><li> Lots of attempts, some frustration, chill beats and more.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A quick use tether that auto targets based on your movement, allowing you to attach to world terrain and tether points.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1d08d6d2928930bc0b3fac4de9988b6a.poster.avif?t=1737487442\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1d08d6d2928930bc0b3fac4de9988b6a.webm?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1d08d6d2928930bc0b3fac4de9988b6a.mp4?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Race against the vines to complete levels before they cover everything.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/478d1db59e93e6cb03039384654e460a.poster.avif?t=1737487442\" width=560 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/478d1db59e93e6cb03039384654e460a.webm?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/478d1db59e93e6cb03039384654e460a.mp4?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Master when to sprint and when not too, saving energy or time.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/a1f7a14d57c5b3b4b55c533c6d73f559.poster.avif?t=1737487442\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/a1f7a14d57c5b3b4b55c533c6d73f559.webm?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/a1f7a14d57c5b3b4b55c533c6d73f559.mp4?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dash over large gaps, while clearing your fall speed.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1766653271ddef752c676508bd4fc590.poster.avif?t=1737487442\" width=482 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1766653271ddef752c676508bd4fc590.webm?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1766653271ddef752c676508bd4fc590.mp4?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Keali includes</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Six to Ten hours of content.<br></li><li> Extra challenges in the form of Mural Fragments that unlock secrets of the past.<br></li><li> Leaderboards to race friends and strangers.<br></li><li> A complex and engaging movement system with a high skill ceiling for you to explore and master.<br></li><li> Unique levels that explore custom platforms, threats, and puzzles.<br></li><li> Levels have multiple solutions, some easier than others.<br></li><li> Lots of attempts, some frustration, chill beats and more.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A quick use tether that auto targets based on your movement, allowing you to attach to world terrain and tether points.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1d08d6d2928930bc0b3fac4de9988b6a.poster.avif?t=1737487442\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1d08d6d2928930bc0b3fac4de9988b6a.webm?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/1d08d6d2928930bc0b3fac4de9988b6a.mp4?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Race against the vines to complete levels before they cover everything.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/478d1db59e93e6cb03039384654e460a.poster.avif?t=1737487442\" width=560 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538780/extras/478d1db59e93e6cb03039384654e460a.webm?t=1737487442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/